	</a>
</div>

<h3 class="regularSummaryHeadline"><a target="_blank" href="/asia-pacific/20200616/north-korea-border-troops/zh-hant/" title="朝鮮爆破開城朝韓聯絡辦公室">朝鮮爆破開城朝韓聯絡辦公室</a></h3>
<h6 class="byline"> <span class="en_byline">CHOE SANG-HUN</span> <span class="time"></span> </h6>
<p class="summary">韓國統一部稍早確認了這一消息。朝韓關係曾一度走向緩和，但朝鮮此舉激烈地表明了近期對韓國的不滿。三天前，金與正警告稱，將看到朝韓聯絡處「完全坍塌的悲慘景象」。</p>
</li><li class="autoListStory "><h4 class="kicker">新聞分析</h4>
<div class="thumbnail">
	  <a href="/asia-pacific/20200615/korea-nuclear-trump-kim/zh-hant/" title="「川金會」兩年後，朝鮮局勢為何仍無解？">
        <img class="img-lazyload" data-url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2020/06/12/us/politics/12dc-korea-assess/12dc-korea-assess-thumbLarge.jpg" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAQAAAC1HAwCAAAAC0lEQVR42mNkYAAAAAYAAjCB0C8AAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="川普總統和朝鮮領導人金正恩去年在非軍事區韓國一側見了面。" width="75" height="75"/>
	</a>
