<h3 class="regularSummaryHeadline"><a target="_blank" href="/asia-pacific/20200615/korea-nuclear-trump-kim/zh-hant/" title="「川金會」兩年後，朝鮮局勢為何仍無解？">「川金會」兩年後，朝鮮局勢為何仍無解？</a></h3>
<h6 class="byline"> <span class="en_byline">DAVID E. SANGER</span>, <span class="en_byline">CHOE SANG-HUN</span> <span class="time"></span> </h6>
<p class="summary">朝鮮稱與美韓尋求和平的希望已「徹底消失」。朝鮮目前的核武庫據信比川普與金正恩首次會晤時要大得多。「川金會」的失敗凸顯了過於依賴首腦之間個人外交的風險。</p>
</li><li class="autoListStory "><h4 class="kicker"></h4>
